   <script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
  
     //Animo i grafici  
	var updatingChart = $(".updating-chart").peity("line", { fill: '#cedac5', stroke:'#ffffff', width: 150, height: 50 })
    var barChart = $(".bar").peity("bar", {  fill: ["#cedac5", "#ffffff"], width: 150, height: 50  })  
    var pieChart = $(".pie").peity("pie", {  fill: ["#cedac5", "#ffffff"], width: 150, height: 50  }) 
        
        
	setInterval(function() {
	  var random = Math.round(Math.random() * 10)
	  var values = updatingChart.text().split(",")
	  values.shift()
	  values.push(random)
	
	  updatingChart
		.text(values.join(","))
		.change()
		
	  barChart
		.text(values.join(","))
		.change()	
		
      
	}, 1000);
   
   //Animo i numeri
   $('.counter').counterUp({
              delay: 10,
              time: 5000
   });
  
});
   </script>

      <script type="text/javascript">
       $script.ready('jquery', function () {
        $script('/CMSScripts/Custom/GlobalScripts/jquery-bxslider-min.js', 'bxslider');
    });



	var _FeedUrl = "http://blog.peoples.it/pokeronline/category/istituzionale/feed/";
	var _MaxCount = parseInt("10");
	var _ShowDesc = "True" == "True" ? true : false;
	var _ShowImage = "True" == "True" ? true : false;
	var _ShowFooter = "True" == "True" ? true : false;
	var _DescCharacterLimit = parseInt("5000");

	var _IdDivRss = "blogFeed";
	var _ClassDivRss = "blogRss";
	var _ContainerUlClass = "blogFeeds";


    //bxslider
	var _Mode = "vertical";
	var _MaxSlides = parseInt("5");
	var _MoveSlides = parseInt("1");
	var _SlideMargin = parseInt("0");
	var _SlideWidth = parseInt("0");
	var _UseCSS = "False" == "True" ? true : false;
	var _Pause = parseInt("4000");
	

	var _slider = null;
	var loader = "<div class=\"mgLoading\"><i class=\"fa fa-spinner fa-spin fa-lg\"></i></div>";

	$mg(document).ready(function () {

	    $script.ready('bxslider', function () {

	        $mg("#" + _IdDivRss).html(loader);

	        var input = { endpoint: _FeedUrl, method: "POST", param: "" };
	        var _endpointProxy = "/UtilityService.svc/RESTfulProxy";

	        $mg.ajax({
	            url: _endpointProxy,
	            contentType: "application/json",
	            type: "POST",
	            data: JSON.stringify(input),
	            complete: function () {
	                //console.log("ok");
	                if (_slider == null) {
	                    _slider = $mg('.' + _ContainerUlClass).bxSlider({
	                        auto: true,
	                        touchEnabled: true,
	                        pager: false,
	                        controls: false,
	                        autoHover: true,
	                        minSlides: 1,
	                        maxSlides: _MaxSlides,
	                        moveSlides: _MoveSlides,
	                        slideMargin: _SlideMargin,
	                        slideWidth: _SlideWidth,
	                        useCSS: _UseCSS,
	                        mode: _Mode,
	                        pause: _Pause
	                    });
	                } else {

	                    _slider.reloadSlider({
	                        auto: true,
	                        touchEnabled: true,
	                        pager: false,
	                        controls: false,
	                        autoHover: true,
	                        minSlides: 1,
	                        maxSlides: _MaxSlides,
	                        moveSlides: _MoveSlides,
	                        slideMargin: _SlideMargin,
	                        slideWidth: _SlideWidth,
	                        useCSS: _UseCSS,
	                        mode: _Mode,
                            pause: _Pause
	                    });
	                }
	            },
	            success: function (t) {
	                var s = "";
	                if (t.Error == null) {
	                    $mg("#" + _IdDivRss).empty();
	                    $mg("#" + _IdDivRss).append('<div class="' + _ContainerUlClass + '">')

	                    var items = $mg($mg.parseXML(t.Result)).find('item');

	                    for (var i = 0; i < _MaxCount && i < items.length; i++) {

	                        var item = $mg(items[i]);

	                        var singleItem = {
	                            title: item.find("title").text(),
	                            link: item.find("link").text(),
	                            description: item.find("description").text().replace(/<(\w+)[^>]*>.*<\/\1>/gi, ""),
	                            pubDate: item.find("pubDate").text(),
	                            author: item.find("author").text() != "" ? item.find("author").text() : item.find("creator").text(),
                                imgSrc : ""
	                        }
                            /*
	                        if (singleItem.description == "") {
	                            singleItem.description = item.find("description").text().replace(/<(\w+)[^>]*>/gi, "").replace(/<\/(\w+)[^>]*>/gi, "");
	                        }
                            */
                            
	                        try{
	                            singleItem.imgSrc = $mg($mg(item.find("encoded").text()).find("img")[0]).prop("src");
	                            if (singleItem.imgSrc == undefined) {
                                    //fix for white firefox and IE
	                                singleItem.imgSrc = $mg($mg(item.find("content\\:encoded").text()).find("img")[0]).prop("src");
	                            }
	                        }
	                        catch(err){ }


	                        if (_ShowDesc) {
	                            if (_DescCharacterLimit > 0 && singleItem.description.length > _DescCharacterLimit) {
	                                singleItem.description = singleItem.description.substr(0, _DescCharacterLimit) + " (...)";
	                            } 
	                        }
	                        else {
	                            singleItem.description = "";
	                        }

	                        var dataFeed = new Date(singleItem.pubDate).toLocaleDateString();
	                        var imageTag = _ShowImage && singleItem.imgSrc != "" && singleItem.imgSrc !== undefined ? "<img src='" + singleItem.imgSrc + "' alt='" + singleItem.title + "' />" : "";
	                        var footer = _ShowFooter ? '<p class="feedFooter"><a title="' + singleItem.title + '" href="' + singleItem.link + '" class="readMore" target="_blank">Continua a leggere &raquo;</a></p>' : "";
	                        var thehtml = '<div class="slide"><h3><a href="' + singleItem.link + '" target="_blank">' + singleItem.title + '</a></h3><p class="publication-date-blog">' + dataFeed + '</p><div class="feed-content">' + imageTag + singleItem.description + '</div>' + footer + '</div>';
	                        $mg("#" + _IdDivRss + " > div ").append(thehtml);
	                    }
                        
	                    $mg("#" + _IdDivRss).append("</div>");

	                }
	            }
	        });

	    });
	});
      </script>

   <script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
	//remove parameters
function removeParameter(paramName) {

       //check for webstorage support
       if (typeof (Storage) !== "undefined") { 
             //check if exists
             if (localStorage.getItem(paramName) != null) {
                    localStorage.removeItem(paramName);
             }
       }
       else {
             //cookie
             $.removeCookie(paramName);
       }
}

//add parameters
function addParameter(paramName, paramValue) {

       //check for webstorage support
       if (typeof (Storage) !== "undefined") {
             localStorage.setItem(paramName, paramValue);
       }
       else {
             //cookie
             $.cookie(paramName, paramValue, { expires: 365 });
       }
}

//get parameters
function getParameter(paramName) {
       //check for webstorage support
       if (typeof (Storage) !== "undefined") {
             return localStorage.getItem(paramName);
       }
       else {
             //cookie
             return $.cookie(paramName);
       }
}

var checkCookieInfo = getParameter("CookieInfo");
	
if(!checkCookieInfo){
		$('#privacyCookie').fadeIn();	
	}else{
		$('#privacyCookie').remove();
	}
	//if close button is clicked
	$('#cookieconfirm').click(function (e) {
		e.preventDefault();
		addParameter("CookieInfo", true);
		$('#privacyCookie').fadeOut();
	});	
});
   </script>
